      "title": "Man caught with Rs.30 mn worth of Ice in Wattala",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Special Task Force (STF) personnel have arrested a 35-year-old man with more than 4 kg of Ice drug (methamphetamine crystal) worth Rs. 30 million in Wattala yesterday.",
        "The drugs were taken into custody while being transported in a car.",
        "He was handed over to the Police Narcotic Bureau for further investigations."
